{"id":232647471,"title":"推薦書籍 環島讀冊","content":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0W.jpg\n\n環島讀冊 作者：曹馥年\n推薦給喜歡看書的人，不喜歡看書的人也很值得看，說不定會有意外的收穫。\n\n這是一本獨立書店的故事，是一本非常棒的書，作者傳達了各家獨立書店的故事，有溫馨的、懷念的、有趣的、奮鬥的、辛酸的、難過的，每間書店都是獨一無二。\n\n我以前買書為了方便，幾乎都是網路買，要不就是去連鎖書店，去獨立書店的次數很少。透過這本書，讓我發現為了方便反而錯過了更多。\n\n可以來場獨立書店旅行了。","excerpt":"環島讀冊 作者：曹馥年，推薦給喜歡看書的人，不喜歡看書的人也很值得看，說不定會有意外的收穫。這是一本獨立書店的故事，是一本非常棒的書，作者傳達了各家獨立書店的故事，有溫馨的、懷念的、有趣的、奮鬥的、辛","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e0a290f4-752b-48a2-a791-f211f8b46588","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-08T08:38:01.039Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-08T08:39:06.123Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["書籍","推薦書單","散文"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"書籍","forumAlias":"book","school":"國立高雄海洋科技大學","department":"輪機工程系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0W.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c677d509-48df-4a2c-b99e-4a0d668e6420","url":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0Wl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0Wl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0Wl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-08T08:39:06.123Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-08T08:39:06.123Z"},{"id":"c677d509-48df-4a2c-b99e-4a0d668e6420","url":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0W.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/vZXed0W","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vZXed0Wl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-08T08:39:06.123Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-08T08:39:06.123Z"}],"postAvatar":""}